  "text": "PLA was purchased from Shenzhen Bright China Inc. (Shenzhen, China). Nanohydroxyapatite rod (nHA) powders were obtained commercially from Nanjing Emperor Nano Materials (Nanjing, China). Graphite flakes were bought from Sigma-Aldrich Inc. (Saint Louis, MO, USA). All reagents such as N,N-dimethylformamide (DMF), dichloromethane (DCM), K 2 MnO 4 , NaNO [CITATION_1] , etc., were used as received.",
